'''[[Cannabis]] in [[Tonga]]''' is illegal, but cultivated illicitly.<ref name="Board2007">{{cite book|author=United Nations: International Narcotics Control Board|title=Report of the International Narcotics Control Board 2006|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qGjTNqElWJoC&pg=PA84|date=February 2007|publisher=United Nations Publications|isbn=978-92-1-148218-8|pages=84–}}</ref> A 1990s report attributed increased cannabis usage in Tonga to foreign travelers and returned Tongan emigres.<ref>{{cite book|title=International Narcotics Control Strategy Report|date=1993|accessdate=7 December 2017}}</ref>

